"Hi!\n"
"You have been invited to the {name} event organizer team - Please click here "
"to accept:\n"
"\n"
"{invitation_link}\n"
"\n"
"See you there,\n"
"The {organizer} team"
msgstr ""
"Hallo!\n"
"Sie wurden zum Event-Organizer-Team für die Veranstaltung {name} eingeladen "
"– bitte hier klicken, um die Einladung anzunehmen:\n"
"\n"
"{invitation_link}\n"
"\n"
"Bis bald\n"
"Das {organizer}-Team"

#: base/models/organizer.py:563
msgid "You have been invited to an organizer team"
msgstr "Sie wurden zu einem Organizer-Team eingeladen"

