#: cfp/templates/cfp/event/user_submission_invitation.html:23
msgid ""
"Invite another speaker to your proposal here. Instead of letting us send an "
"email, (which might get caught by spam filters) you can also give them this "
"link:"
msgstr ""
"Laden Sie hier eine weitere Vortragende ein. Statt eine Mail schicken zu "
"lassen (die vielleicht im Spam-Filter landet), können Sie der betreffenden "
