#: control/templates/pretixcontrol/email/forgot.txt:1
#, python-format
msgid ""
"Hello,\n"
"\n"
"you requested a new password. Please go to the following page to reset your "
"password:\n"
"\n"
"%(url)s\n"
"\n"
"Best regards,\n"
"Your system team\n"
msgstr ""
"Hallo,\n"
"\n"
"Sie haben ein neues Passwort angefordert. Bitte rufen Sie die folgende Seite "
"auf, um Ihr Passwort zurückzusetzen:\n"
"\n"
"%(url)s\n"
"\n"
"Mit freundlichen Grüßen\n"
"Ihr Systemteam\n"

#: control/templates/pretixcontrol/email/invitation.txt:1
#, python-format
msgid ""
"Hello,\n"
"\n"
"You have been added to the following event team:\n"
"\n"
"Organizer: %(organizer)s\n"
"Team: %(team)s\n"
"\n"
"Click the following link to view your team dashboard:\n"
"\n"
"%(url)s\n"
"\n"
"Best regards,\n"
"\n"
"Your event team\n"
msgstr ""
"Hallo,\n"
"\n"
"Sie wurden dem folgenden Event-Team hinzugefügt:\n"
"\n"
"Veranstalter: %(organizer)s\n"
"Team: %(team)s\n"
"\n"
"Klicken Sie auf den folgenden Link, um Ihr Team-Dashboard anzuzeigen:\n"
"\n"
"%(url)s\n"
"\n"
"Mit freundlichen Grüßen\n"
"\n"
"Ihr Event-Team\n"

#: control/templates/pretixcontrol/email/invitation.txt:15
#, python-format
msgid ""
"Hello,\n"
"\n"
"You have been invited to the following event team:\n"
"\n"
"Organizer: %(organizer)s\n"
"Team: %(team)s\n"
"\n"
"If you want to join that team, just click on the following link:\n"
"\n"
"%(url)s\n"
"\n"
"If you do not want to join, you can safely ignore or delete this email.\n"
"\n"
"Best regards,\n"
"\n"
"Your event team\n"
msgstr ""
"Hallo,\n"
"\n"
"Sie wurden in das folgende Event-Team eingeladen:\n"
"\n"
"Veranstalter: %(organizer)s\n"
"Team: %(team)s\n"
"\n"
"Wenn Sie diesem Team beitreten möchten, klicken Sie einfach auf den "
"folgenden Link:\n"
"\n"
"%(url)s\n"
"\n"
"Wenn Sie nicht beitreten möchten, können Sie diese E-Mail ignorieren oder "
"löschen.\n"
"\n"
"Mit freundlichen Grüßen\n"
"\n"
"Ihr Event-Team\n"

#: control/templates/pretixcontrol/email/security_notice.txt:1
#, python-format
msgid ""
"Hello,\n"
"\n"
"this is to inform you that the account information of your eventyay account "
"has been\n"
"changed. In particular, the following changes have been performed:\n"
"\n"
"%(messages)s\n"
"\n"
"If this change was not performed by you, please contact us immediately.\n"
"\n"
"You can review and change your account settings here:\n"
"\n"
"%(url)s\n"
"\n"
"Best regards,\n"
"Your system team\n"
msgstr ""
"Hallo,\n"
"\n"
"dies dient zur Information, dass die Kontoinformationen Ihres eventyay-"
"Kontos geändert wurden. Insbesondere wurden die folgenden Änderungen "
"vorgenommen:\n"
"\n"
"%(messages)s\n"
"\n"
"Wenn diese Änderung nicht von Ihnen vorgenommen wurde, kontaktieren Sie uns "
"bitte umgehend.\n"
"\n"
"Sie können Ihre Kontoeinstellungen hier einsehen und ändern:\n"
"\n"
"%(url)s\n"
"\n"
"Mit freundlichen Grüßen\n"
"Ihr Systemteam\n"

